&lt;p&gt;sorry, you can close this issue!&lt;br/&gt;
The problem was in front of the computer. &lt;br/&gt;
The Xerces library for castor was not found.&lt;br/&gt;
I have attached the lib to dependencies and all works fine.&lt;br/&gt;
The problem was you could only find the problem with maven in debug mode.&lt;/p&gt;


